  <section class="section" id="install">
    <div class="section-label">Installation</div>
    <h2>Get started in minutes</h2>
    <div class="install-steps">
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">1</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Download the latest release</h4>
          <p>Download the latest <a href="{{ site.downloadUrl }}">PointsHarvest-{{ site.extensionVersion }}.zip</a> and extract it.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">2</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Load into Chrome</h4>
          <p>Navigate to <code>chrome://extensions</code>, enable <strong>Developer mode</strong> (top right), then click <strong>Load unpacked</strong> and select the extracted folder.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="step">
        <div class="step-num">3</div>
        <div class="step-body">
          <h4>Run it</h4>
          <p>Open <a href="https://rewards.bing.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">rewards.bing.com</a>, make sure you're signed into your Microsoft account, then click the Points Harvest icon in Chrome and hit <strong>Run today's searches</strong>.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="margin-top: 1.25rem; font-size: 0.88rem; color: var(--muted);">First time? Read the <a href="/blog/getting-started/"><strong>full getting started guide</strong></a> for detailed instructions, pop-up permissions setup, and tips.</p>
